title: [Fired Up, Front Room]
description: Paneled in oak, the lofty walls are lined with shelves displaying a variety of collectibles and earthenware.  A beeswax candle-laden corona of brass is suspended from a thick monir beam overhead, illuminating an enormous totem pole laying on its side down the length of the wagon.
location: between Wehnimer's Landing and Zul Logoth
